description.fr: Depuis l'enlèvement de {God:2} par un mystérieux Shushu, {CharacterName:474} se sent investie d'une grande mission\_: retrouver et protéger les dieux du Monde des Douze\_! Elle a ainsi rassemblé toutes les connaissances les concernant à la tour d'{CharacterName:1025}.
description.en: Ever since {God:2} was kidnapped by a mysterious Shushu, {CharacterName:474} has been on a mission to find and protect the World of Twelve's gods! She has therefore collected all knowledge about them in {CharacterName:1025}'s tower.
description.es: Desde el secuestro de {God:2} por un misterioso fab'huritu. {CharacterName:474} se ve enfrascada en una gran misión: ¡encontrar y proteger a los dioses del Mundo de los Doce! Así que ha reunido todos sus conocimientos centrándolos en la torre de {CharacterName:1025}.
description.de: Nachdem {God:2} von einem mysteriösen Shushu entführt wurde, hat sich {CharacterName:474} einer großen Mission verschrieben: Sie will die Götter der Welt der Zwölf finden und beschützen! Dazu hat sie sich im Turm von {CharacterName:1025} das nötige Wissen angeeignet.
description.pt: Desde o sequestro de {God:2} por um misterioso Shushu, {CharacterName:474} se sente incumbida de uma grande missão: encontrar e proteger os deuses do Mundo dos Doze! Assim, ela reuniu todo o conhecimento sobre eles na torre de {CharacterName:1025}.

descriptionFinished.fr: Alors qu'{CharacterName:474} passe en revue chaque dieu au Bibliotemple, {CharacterName:873} surgit en panique : son phorreur {CharacterName:175} a disparu\_!
descriptionFinished.en: While {CharacterName:474} was reviewing each god at the Temple of Scriptures, {CharacterName:873} showed up suddenly in a panic. His drheller, {CharacterName:175}, has disappeared!
descriptionFinished.es: Mientras que {CharacterName:474} examina a cada dios en el bibliotemplo, {CharacterName:873} aparece aterrorizado: ¡su perforatroz {CharacterName:175} ha desaparecido!
descriptionFinished.de: Als {CharacterName:474} alle Götter noch mal im Bibliotempel durchgeht, stürmt ein von Panik getriebener {CharacterName:873} herein: sein Griesgrab {CharacterName:175} ist verschwunden!
descriptionFinished.pt: Enquanto {CharacterName:474} revisa cada deus no Bibliotemplo, {CharacterName:873} surge em pânico: seu Perfuratroz {CharacterName:175} desapareceu!
